data.description: 2219 Wightman Street presents the opportunity to purchase your next home or an investment property, with a current lease in place which expires in May of 2024.  This charming property has a front covered porch, perfect for socializing with neighbors and friends, as well as a rear deck that overlooks the fenced-in back yard and gardens. The interior is bright and cheerful with lots of windows that allow natural light to flood the space. There is a full bath on the main level, and an additional bath and three bedrooms on the second. The partially finished walkout basement has a large laundry and a cozy den to watch movies. While there is ample parking on Wightman Street, the property also includes a designated parking spot accessible from Melvin Street. Its prime location near universities, hospitals, Squirrel Hill Shopping and Schenley Park makes it an ideal investment opportunity. Plus, with so many fun activities within walking distance, tenants will never run out of things to do.
